Total mortality z

Source: R/genericMethods.R, R/FLS.R
z-methods.Rd

Returns the calculation of total mortality, z, usually as the sum of fishing mortality, f, and natural mortality, m.

Usage

z(object, ...)

# S4 method for FLS
z(object, ...)

Arguments

object

Object to calculate on.

...

Any extra arguments.

Value

An object of the corresponding class, usually FLQuant.

See also

FLQuant

Author

The FLR Team

Examples

data(ple4)

z(ple4)
